Description:
Heritage 2022 (ICC21 LL-08 2104) is a non-dividend paying 
whole life insurance policy designed to give the client the 
most death benefit for each premium dollar spent.;
POLICY MATURITY=Age 121;

Underwriting classes and process:
Underwriting Class=Preferred Plus NT, Preferred NT, Standard Plus NT,
Standard NT, Preferred T, Standard T;
Table Rates= Tables 1 (A) to 16 (P);

Description:
Description and details=Income Advantage Indexed Universal Life (IUL) offers flexible protection with the potential for cash value growth linked to indexed strategies. This product includes features such as a guaranteed refund option, lapse guard protection, and a wash loan feature in later years. The policy matures at age 120 and allows for multiple index crediting strategies to suit various investment preferences;
Policy Exclusions and Limitations=
The death benefit will not be paid if the insured?s death results from suicide, while sane
or insane, within two years from the date of issue. Instead, we will pay the sum of the
premiums paid since issue, less any loan and loan interest due and any withdrawals.
Exclusions and limitations may vary by state.;
Policy Maturity Age= The policy will mature at age 120. Upon maturity, if the insured is still living, the surrender
value will be paid.;

