CONVERSION =Conversion to any permanent life plan is available during the Initial Term (but not beyond age 65). Please see TERM CONVERSIONS, Page B-44 for additional information. There will be full first year commissions paid on the first year premium for the new permanent life plan minus the full first year commissions on the converted Centennial Term;
CONVERSION CREDIT = The first premium for the new permanent plan will be reduced by a conversion credit equal in amount to the sum of the premiums paid for the base term plan in the last 12 months on the converted amount;

